    </a></div></div></div> <div class="flair-container" data-v-3cb16c5a><div data-v-3cb16c5a><!----> <div data-v-3cb16c5a><article class="blog-markdown mx-auto max-w-screen-md prose prose-hr:h-[8px] prose-hr:m-0 prose-hr:border-none prose-headings:my-0 prose-headings:font-700 prose-headings:text-charcoal prose-h1:mb-[32px] prose-h1:mt-[48px] prose-h1:text-[34px] prose-h1:leading-[40px] prose-h1:tracking-[0.25px] md:prose-h1:text-[48px] md:prose-h1:leading-[56px] md:prose-h1:tracking-[0px] lg:prose-h1:text-[60px] lg:prose-h1:leading-[72px] prose-h2:text-[24px] prose-h2:leading-[32px] prose-h2:tracking-[0px] prose-h2:mt-[48px] prose-h2:mb-[24px] md:prose-h2:text-[34px] md:prose-h2:leading-[40px] md:prose-h2:tracking-[0.25px] lg:prose-h2:text-[40px] lg:prose-h2:leading-[48px] lg:prose-h2:tracking-[0px] prose-h3:text-[20px] prose-h3:leading-[32px] prose-h3:tracking-[0.15px] prose-h3:mb-[20px] md:prose-h3:text-[24px] md:prose-h3:leading-[32px] md:prose-h3:tracking-[0px] prose-p:m-0 prose-p:font-500 prose-p:text-charcoal prose-p:text-[14px] prose-p:leading-[24px] prose-p:tracking-[0.1px] prose-p:mb-[20px] md:prose-p:text-[16px] md:prose-p:leading-[32px] md:prose-p:tracking-[0.15px] prose-a:text-blue prose-strong:font-700 prose-blockquote:border-none prose-blockquote:relative prose-p:before:content-[] prose-blockquote:not-italic prose-blockquote:m-0 prose-blockquote:p-[8px_0px_8px_16px] md:prose-blockquote:p-[8px_0px_8px_26px] prose-blockquote:before:absolute prose-blockquote:before:inset-0 prose-blockquote:before:w-[4px] prose-blockquote:before:bg-blue prose-blockquote:before:rounded-full prose-blockquote:before:left-0 md:prose-blockquote:before:w-[6px] prose-ol:pl-[16px] prose-ol:mb-[20px] prose-ol:list-decimal md:prose-ol:pl-[26px] prose-li:marker:proportional-nums prose-ul:pl-[16px] prose-ul:mb-[20px] prose-ul:list-disc md:prose-ul:pl-[26px] prose-li:font-500 prose-li:text-charcoal prose-li:text-[16px] prose-li:leading-[32px] prose-li:m-0 prose-li:p-0 prose-table:table-fixed prose-table:border-[0px] prose-table:text-charcoal prose-table:text-[14px] prose-table:leading-[24px] md:prose-table:text-[16px] prose-tr:grid prose-tr:divide-y-[3px] prose-tr:divide-lavender prose-tr:border-[0px] sm:prose-tr:border-[3px] sm:prose-tr:border-lavender sm:prose-tr:table-row prose-td:p-[32px] sm:prose-td:border-[3px] sm:prose-td:border-lavender prose-th:p-[32px] empty:prose-th:hidden sm:empty:prose-th:table-cell sm:prose-th:border-[3px] sm:prose-th:border-lavender prose-thead:border-[3px] prose-thead:border-lavender prose-tbody:border-[3px] prose-tbody:border-lavender prose-tbody:divide-y-[3px] prose-tbody:divide-lavender"><h2 id="whatisajobdescription">What Is A Job Description?</h2>
<p>A&#xA0;<strong><a href="/en/blog/job-description" rel="noopener">job description</a></strong>&#xA0;or &quot;JD&quot; is a written document that describes the primary responsibilities, general tasks, and other necessary duties carried out by a particular position. Your JD is the most vital part of the recruitment process.</p>
<p>A&#xA0;job description&#xA0;also shares details about the company, its mission, <a href="/en/blog/corporate-culture" rel="noopener">culture</a>, benefits, salary and sets the expectations for the role. It needs to provide enough detail so&#xA0;job seekers&#xA0;can decide whether or not they are qualified for the position and get them interested in applying.</p>
<p>Writing a captivating&#xA0;job description&#xA0;is essential to attract the best candidates. This is your opportunity to market your company and the vacant position to your future hire and stand out from the millions of other&#xA0;job postings&#xA0;on the internet.</p>
<p>Want to easily track your applicants throughout the recruitment process? flair's <a href="/en/products/recruiting" rel="noopener">recruiting</a> feature can help you keep your candidates' data organized.</p>
</article></div> <!----> <!----></div><div data-v-3cb16c5a><!----> <!----> <!----> <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto my-[20px] min-h-[180px] h-[180px] overflow-hidden rounded-[5px] md:min-h-[340px] md:h-[340px] lg:min-h-[400px] lg:h-[400px] md:rounded-[10px] lg:my-[40px] inner-img:w-full inner-img:h-full inner-img:object-cover" data-v-3cb16c5a><picture><source media="(min-width: 1280px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1336x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/2672x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1336x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg, https://img2.storyblok.com/2672x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg 2x"><source media="(min-width: 1024px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1176x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/2352x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1176x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg, https://img2.storyblok.com/2352x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg 2x"><source media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/920x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f695c8/retail-employee-job-description-blog-1.jpeg 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/1840x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/6720x4480/55b6f69