<p>These shared skills and competencies are often found among successful retail employees:</p>
<ul>
<li>Great&#xA0;communication skills</li>
<li>Goal-oriented</li>
<li>Friendly</li>
<li>Energetic</li>
<li>Persuasive</li>
<li>Customer service skills</li>
<li>Multitasking skills</li>
<li>Time management skills</li>
</ul>
